availabilityZone.description: The availability zone in which to place the request.

instanceType.description: The type of instance to request.

priority.description: The priority for the launch template override. The lower the number, the higher the priority. If no number is set, the launch template override has the lowest priority.

spotPrice.description: The maximum spot bid for this override request.

subnetId.description: The subnet in which to launch the requested instance.

weightedCapacity.description: The capacity added to the fleet by a fulfilled request.
